        </h2><img src="https://www.kct.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Mask-Group-4.png" width="100%">
        <div>
        <p>Mahatma Gandhi Central Library is housed in the first floor of Dr. Mahalingam Vigyan Bhavan with large, open spaces, niches for collaborative work, open access system, creatively designed work platforms and an infusion of natural and architectural aesthetics unfolding new learning paths for everyone—student, scholar, researcher, teacher, visitor or just a curious mind.</p>
